data.description: This unique townhome has been meticulously maintained and offers everything you want and more! Conveniently located right off I-295 close to shops and restaurants, the Mayport Naval Station, and across the street from the Jacksonville Arboretum and Botanical Gardens. A private courtyard entry welcomes you to this spacious floorplan featuring an attached garage, fully fenced in backyard, and elegant upgrades throughout! Give up yardwork and just enjoy gardening in your turf-filled/fully-fenced backyard which also offers a large screened-in lanai and composite wood deck. Kitchen features updated fixtures, stainless steel GE appliances, refinished countertops, and a large breakfast bar perfect for entertaining guests. Spacious great room contains walnut laminate wood flooring and wood-burnin g fireplace. All ensuite bathrooms have been wonderfully renovated with updated vanities, ceramic flooring, and a stunning pebble tile walk-in shower. Call today for your own private tour before it's gone!
